      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "BIRDSONG (5) has won her two starts at this circuit and distance in emphatic style, last time overcoming a back row draw. Hard to knock and can maintain the perfect record. MAC TILLY (3) opened her career in pleasing fashion last start, coming from this barrier for a 3.6m third at Wagga. Open to natural improvement. ATOMIK GO ANNA (4) is by top sire Art Major and hails from the Tom Gilligan stable. Has been showing some ability at the trials wins so anticipating a good start to her career. KISS BEFORE TWELVE (6) is also at the track for the first time. By Capt Midnight and hails from the Clayton Harmey stable. Draws wide but has good trial form coming into this so keep safe.",
